*Mamom* je ostavio poruku da dođe kući. (He left a message for his mom to come home.) 

Kćerke su se *mamom* radovale. (The daughters were delighted with their mom.) 

*Mamom* je bilo veoma teško da se oprosti od svoje dece. (It was very hard for her mom to say goodbye to her children.) 

Nakon što je *mamom* ušao u sobu, deca su počela da se smeju. (Once mom entered the room, the children started laughing.) 

*Mamom* je bio potreban dodatni novac za održavanje kuće. (Mom needed extra money to maintain the house.)